            <div class="key-row"><kbd>空格</kbd><span>硬降</span></div>
            <div class="key-row"><kbd>P</kbd><span>暂停</span></div>
            <div class="key-row"><kbd>R</kbd><span>重新开始</span></div>
          </div>
